Usage: reportWirePath [-help] [-detail] -end <string> [-include_pin]
                      -start <string> [-tcl  [-no_output ]]

-help               # Prints out the command usage
-detail             # Specify whether to print detail information of the path
                    # (bool, optional)
-end <string>       # Specify end term name (string, required)
-include_pin        # Specify whether to include pin in report (bool, optional)
-no_output          # Specify whether to print the path when -tcl is specified
                    # (bool, optional)
-start <string>     # Specify start term name (string, required)
-tcl                # Specify whether return tcl dict of the wire path
                    # (bool, optional)